text: <!channel>: We just slated a LARGE event for Hispanicpros on February 26th from 5:30-8:30pm.  It will take up all of 390 and will need some setup. Unfortunately <@U026NB2U2> and I will be at Intel all day and not sure when we will be back. Would anyone like to volunteer?
I can def. help out with this one.
AWESOME <@U02618EV1> - we'll most likely have a preliminary planning session so I'll keep you in the loop.
<@U02HCCTFL>: By any chance are any of the guys you met with connected to SW Portland Latino?
Coincidentally I was going to send them an email today/tomorrow about volunteering for the event.
I think I'm going to be a mentor - Marce will most likely be involved as well :simple_smile:
yes, I'm in for that one. In June I believe. Juan Barraza is planning
it's now on team cal (and mine) if anyone wants to copy it over
Thanks for the info <@U02HCCTFL>. Will definitely reach out to Juan.
late to this thread, but I'll be there
We should also send someone to this: <https://www.portlandoregon.gov/bps/article/517228>
